{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/14", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/14/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/14/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/14/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/kemu3007/portal/issues/14", "id": 1167568913, "node_id": "I_kwDOG7qoq85Fl7AR", "number": 14, "title": "在Angular中使用Google Adsense", "user": {"login": "kemu3007", "id": 29157528, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTU3NTI4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/29157528?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007", "html_url": "https://github.com/kemu3007", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kemu3007/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 3898939400, "node_id": "LA_kwDOG7qoq87oZRgI", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/labels/article", "name": "article", "color": "C200E5", "default": false, "description": ""}, {"id": 3900074882, "node_id": "LA_kwDOG7qoq87odmuC", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/labels/Angular", "name": "Angular", "color": "D93F0B", "default": false, "description": ""}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2022-03-13T12:39:35Z", "updated_at": "2022-03-13T15:28:08Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "在普通SSR中，可以在`<head> </head>`中分发广告并将自动广告脚本获利。\r\n\r\n但是，就水疗中心而言，如果仅使用自动广告，则不会重新加载页面过渡，因此显示的广告数量（例如页面底部只有固定的广告）通常会减少。\r\n\r\n因此，您可以使用[ng2-adsense]（https://www.npmjs.com/package/package/ng2-adsense）手动配置广告框架。\r\n\r\n### ng2-adsense简介\r\n\r\n环境：Angular V13\r\n\r\n1.`npm安装ng2-adsense`\r\n\r\n2.在`app.module.ts`（链接到要显示ADS的组件或创建用于常用的模块的模块）中描述设置。）\r\n\r\n``TS\r\n@ngmodule（{\r\n  声明：[AppComponent]，\r\n  导入：[[\r\n    browsermodule，\r\n    批准模块，\r\n    adsensemodule.forroot（{adclient：'ca-pub- **************\r\n  ]，，，\r\n  提供者：[]，\r\n  Bootstrap：[AppComponent]，\r\n}）\r\n导出类AppModule {}\r\n````````\r\n\r\n4.添加要在要显示的区域中显示的布局组件\r\n\r\n````html\r\n<ng2-adsense\r\n  样式=“显示：块”\r\n  adformat =“流体”\r\n  插槽=“ ********”\r\n  layoutkey =“ **********”\r\n> </ng2-adsense>\r\n````````\r\n\r\n使用Google Adsense设置的设置进行设置，例如Layoutkey。\r\n\r\n！[image]（https：//user-migs.githubusercontent.com/29157528/158059598-F309054A-618F-46AA-AAA-AAA80-B01392A3A3A3A3A3A3A3A3A3A3AG）\r\n\r\n！[image]（https：//user-bimages.githubusercontent.com/29157528/158059662-BFD1A4D8-778C-4E6C-4E6C-83DB0E7C8402.PNG）\r\n\r\n支持 ^中显示的插槽。\r\n\r\n您可以通过设置以上显示广告。\r\n\r\n我希望在水疗中心提供自动广告，但是考虑到夹在页面过渡之间的广告，我觉得这似乎有些苛刻。", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/14/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/14/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}